<td class="postcell">
<div>
    <div class="post-text" itemprop="description">
        <p>I've been a professional web developer for about five years now, and have compiled many many things for servers. I've also written many simple C programs (one or two files).</p>

<p>The main thing which has held me back from creating more complex applications is the fear of learning to the GNU build tools. The documentation is huge and a bit intimidating.</p>

<p>Does anyone have a good resource to learn these?</p>

    </div>
    <div class="post-taglist">
