<td class="answercell">
    <div class="post-text"><p>Mostly by editing broken Makefiles. :)</p>

<p>The other answers here are quite good, but you can write <code>Makefile.am</code> templates for Automake without having to have a deep knowledge of how to write Makefiles (arguably that's the point). I'm using Automake for my current project, and I haven't had to do much makefile editing (or even reading) to get stuff to work.</p>
</div>
