<td class="answercell">
    <div class="post-text"><p>I have a suggestion. Do not go to the GNU make tutorial directly. It is vast, and as a beginner one can get a setback. </p>

<p>What i suggest is, you start by googling on the web by keyword like "GNU make" or "Understanding makefile". You will get a lot of simple tutorials which are simple and easy. </p>

<p>Once you get a hand in that, and master it, then you can go to the GNU make tutorials to enhance and add more flavours to your current knowledge.</p>

<p>P.S: This is how i started and learnt a lot</p>
</div>
    <table class="fw">
